text: "This Is Me" is a song sang by Demi Lovato and Joe Jonas. It is from the 2008 television movie Camp Rock. It was written and produced by Adam Watts and Andy Dodd. The song was on the Camp Rock soundtrack and was released as a single. ==Charts== Chart (2008) Peak position Chilean Singles ChartChilean Singles Chart. Issue date: October 25, 2008.
